result.name: Daimaru Ramen

reviews.text: Ordered the recommended soup option. The soup is light & almost too weak for my personal taste, I'm more to full body & strong flavor soup taste kinda guy. noodles have options thin or thick, I choose thick as usual, the but noodles don't have distinct flavors. Friendly & very helpful staff, very clean place & comfortable.

Ordered "Black" and "Shrimp". The broth of "Black" is rich and authentic. The "Shrimp" broth carry strong taste of shrimp, it is not my favourite but still tastes nice. They provide self-serving tea, which I think is better than iced water. The shop is neat and comfortable, making us feel like eating in Japan. (No service charge required)
The soup and the meat are yummy. You can choose less oil for the soup and the noodles type 👍🏻. If it allow us to choose the hardness of the noodles, it’s perfect! Nice service as well
I do miss the torching of the char siu as a finishing touch... But I love everything else about this place 👍

Tonkotsu soup is not thick but still rich in flavors. However the sakura shrimp is tasteless under such strong tonkotsu soup so it is not recommended. Soft-boiled egg is well seasoned with Japanese soy sauce and chashuu is good. The noodle is a bit soft and lack of texture.

reviews.text: Ordered the recommended soup option. The soup is light & almost too weak for my personal taste, I'm more to full body & strong flavor soup taste kinda guy. noodles have options thin or thick, I choose thick as usual, the but noodles don't have distinct flavors. Friendly & very helpful staff, very clean place & comfortable.

Ordered "Black" and "Shrimp". The broth of "Black" is rich and authentic. The "Shrimp" broth carry strong taste of shrimp, it is not my favourite but still tastes nice. They provide self-serving tea, which I think is better than iced water. The shop is neat and comfortable, making us feel like eating in Japan. (No service charge required)
喜歡圍住吧台食拉麵的氣氛，服務好，拉麵也不錯，麵爽湯甜，質素比很多出名的拉麵店～ 希望可以好好經營下去
正宗日本北海道拉麵， 靚仔靚女夫妻 中日合璧， 價錢公道， 美味。 值得推介 !

開業約半年，裝修簡樸舒服，整齊清潔，坐位12個，由日本夫妻主理。主打四款拉麵 (可選粗/幼麵，小油/普通/多油)，一款餃子 (自家製，三款醬汁選擇)，專心做食物。
首次試食，喜出望外。選了蝦豚骨拉麵，選粗麵及普通油份。湯味濃郁，不會感肥膩，蝦分量頗多，溫泉蛋很香滑，重醬油味。麵質起初有微韌，但至中期爽口，完全配合喜歡吃爽麵人士，若鍾愛軟些人士建議選幼麵。
餃子新鮮用機煎，很熱，外脆內較，肉汁鮮香，很日式地道風味，5隻$35也很經濟。
服務員友善及主動協助掛起外套，但不設加一服務，值得加分。

Highly recommended this Japanese noodles restaurant which is held by one Japanese couple. Food are specialised in Japanese favoured. Service is great and environment is tidy & clean. No need for 10% service charge. 👍
